Subject: [PATCH] (Yukigram) Metadata

---
 Telegram/CMakeLists.txt                                |  4 ++--
 Telegram/SourceFiles/boxes/about_box.cpp               |  2 +-
 Telegram/SourceFiles/core/version.h                    |  4 ++--
 Telegram/SourceFiles/intro/intro_start.cpp             |  2 +-
 .../settings/sections/settings_notifications.cpp       |  2 +-
 Telegram/SourceFiles/window/main_window.cpp            |  2 +-
